# =============================================================
# ÖZEL İZİN VERİLENLER (whitelist — repo'ya commit OLUR)
# =============================================================

# Briefing ve doküman dosyaları
!handoff/*.md
!.claude/agents/*.md
!.claude/state/*.md
!agent_outputs/*.md
!Modul_A_Critical_Path_Dependency*.md
!*.md
!README.md
!LICENSE

# Critical path JSON'ları (bu özel olarak izin verildi)
!data/manifest.json
!data/layers.json
!reports/kpi.json
!reports/metrics_5fold.json
!reports/threshold_curve.json
!data/labels/blok_cv_split.json

# Requirements
!**/requirements.txt
!**/requirements*.txt
!**/pyproject.toml
!**/setup.py
!**/setup.cfg
!**/Pipfile

# Shell pipeline
!**/run_pipeline.sh
!**/*.sh

# Agent output küçük dosyalar
!agent_outputs/*.md
